%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%

sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor PM as Requestor / Project Manager
participant UI as Vendor Management UI
participant BFF as Vendor BFF
participant CACHE as Redis Cache
participant VMS as Vendor Management Service
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS Read schema"}

PM ->> UI: Click vendor past score / history
UI ->> BFF: Get vendor history(vendorId)

BFF ->> CACHE: Get vendor history cache
alt Cache Hit
    CACHE -->> BFF: Cached last 3 evaluations
else Cache Miss
    BFF ->> VMS: getVendorHistory(vendorId)
    VMS ->> READDB: GET vendor identity
    VMS ->> READDB: GET last 3 evaluations ORDER BY evaluation_date DESC
    VMS ->> READDB: GET past average score and past DRE score
    READDB -->> VMS: Vendor history records
    VMS -->> BFF: Vendor history response
    BFF ->> CACHE: Cache vendor history
end

BFF -->> UI: Open modal with vendor name, ID, avg score, DRE score, last 3 evaluations
PM ->> UI: Close modal